                <description>Further adaptation to this hoof has restored the fingers to a more anthropomorphic state, restoring dexterity.</description>
            </li>
        </stages>
        <comps>
            <li Class="Pawnmorph.Hediffs.CompProperties_MutationSeverityAdjust">
